SELECT
  id,
  argMax(name, time) AS name,
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    [],
    toUInt32(dateDiff('month', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(count,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('month', toDate('2015-1-1'), time))) AS count
FROM
(
  SELECT id, argMax(name, time) AS name, time, arrayMap(x -> x, groupArrayInsertAt(0, 168)(count, toUInt32((day - 1) * 24 + hour))) AS count
  FROM
  (
    SELECT
      toStartOfMonth(created_at) AS time,
      org_id AS id, argMax(org_login, time) AS name,
      toHour(created_at) AS hour,
      toDayOfWeek(created_at) AS day,
      COUNT() AS count
    FROM gh_events
    WHERE  created_at >= toDate('2015-1-1') AND created_at < dateAdd(month, 1, toDate('2016-12-1')) AND (org_id IN [1342004])
    GROUP BY id, time, hour, day
    ORDER BY day, hour
  )
  GROUP BY id, time
  
)
GROUP BY id
ORDER BY count[-1][1] DESC
    LIMIT 3
